/0/description": "During the many years I have worked with Surat,I have always valued him as a highly professional individual .A strong and passionate leader of an extensive FB team. Great trainer , committed to get the job done and not shy to take risks. Creative, quality oriented, supportive and action driven. Fun  to work with.\n \n \n\n \n", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Rudolf Borgesius", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "1st", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rudolf-borgesius-94773610/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAI-dMcB53j-Qmit7qDtCtbEXgMTPNTlaxk", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Somphop managed Surat directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "April 16, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Creative thinker, easy to work with.\nAlways adapting the act or process to suit with business trend with entrepreneur mindset", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Somphop Prattranasanti", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Hotel Manager at Le Meridien Phuket Beach Resort", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/somphop-prattranasanti-845837106/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABrR5vUBzfmQqUmfSWr1fAc6cmNykrKdPL0", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Grégory managed Surat directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "June 26, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Surat is a hard worker and very diligent. I had the pleasure to work with him for more than 2 years in Phuket. He shown a great team spirit and has lot of energy.  ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Grégory Ernoult", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Founding Managing Director at Bencoolen", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/grégory-ernoult-2620a810/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAImIWoBJvMSLZMmh34VDLSoD_7najoTLDw", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Jean-Charles was senior to Surat but didn't manage Surat directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "June 8, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Surat is energetic and gets things done while maintaining standards.\nHe was a very strong part of the F&B team back in 1998-2000 at Novotel Phuket Resort.\nIt was a pleasure to work with him.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Jean-Charles Le Coz", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Bridging gaps between France and Indonesia", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jean-charleslecoz/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEWA4EB5_d1df-onbohXNbF2UuLNlA7szY", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Robert worked with Surat on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "December 9, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Working alongside Khun Surat was a great pleasure.  He is a positive minded, highly creative individual, able to motivate several departments to achieve a common goal. Highlights were his creativity in organizing Halloweem, Loy Kratong, Christmas and Chinese New Year events. Khun Surat is also a great listener and storyteller  in case of conflict between associates.  Simply said Khun Surat is a great team player!", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Robert Wittebrood", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "General Manager The Westin Grande Sukhumvit, Bangkok", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-wittebrood-75a02029/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAXgNjYB3UkchunRCMEm3HGnqk6J6CbwA5I", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Martin managed Surat directly", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "December 9, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "It is my great pleasure to issue this recommendation to Mr. Surat Kanthanakit, who was the F&B Manager during my time as EAM in Dusit Laguna Resort Phuket. \n\nKhun Surat has not only a very pleasant personality to work with, but he has also played a prominent role in establishing the F&B operation as one of the best in the Laguna and in Phuket. He has been able to implement some outstanding standards in the service and food and beverage department alike.\n \nKhun Surat can be counted on all the time, and I have come to appreciate especially his creativity and his commitment to accomplish his tasks with care and dedication, especially after Tsunami were Surat played a vital role in re-opening several outlets and establishing new concepts which proved to be very successful.\n\n I can highly recommend Surat to any employer and wish him only the best for his future career and continuous personal happiness. I would be very pleased to work with him again if our pats would cross again.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Martin Heiniger", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "General Manager The Tongsai Bay", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/martin-heiniger-6b63b141/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAjHeaoBVWNMxenzq3gsbFYmMQSolZdTNJ0", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Laddawan worked with Surat on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "December 7, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "Khun Surat, is one of the best colleague I ever worked with and is also a very good friend of mine.. Khun Surat, is very hard working individual, very creative, extremely dynamic and full of ideas innovations, reliable and very trust worthy.  He also is a great team player, leader and a good conducter, good trainer to his F&B team.. He is one very remarkable and a special person...", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Laddawan Somniyam (Schülke)", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Open for new opportunity", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/laddawan-somniyam-schülke-ba577b1a/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQHe-0BWhZoWSXTi2hPTTBEl-4CWG12Nx4", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Holger worked with Surat but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "December 28, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "Surat showed great service attitude, high energy and an outstanding Can-Do spirit. His lead and direction of the F&B Team greatly supported the requirements of our customers leading to a flawless operational execution.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Holger Jakobs", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Vice President Sales and Marketing at Wharf Hotels Management Limited", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/holger-jakobs-220a88/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAotzgBY8JTLY9fK_NdAgjNOnapqgSRAEA", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Andrew worked with Surat on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "November 12, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "Surat is a dedicated manager who pays attention to detail. He is well liked by his staff and he connects well with them. He has always demonstrated passion for his work and is very creative.", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Andrew Cornelio", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "General Manager leading hospitality excellence at Le Clef Bangkok by The Crest Collection", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrewcornelio/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALPt2MBIS_D3-ITUFf53UqKjZWG91MTIDQ", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Jorge managed Surat directly", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "November 10, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "Results orientated, creative, possessing a can-do attitude. Hands on, practical, leads from the front. No hesitation whatsoever in recommending K Surat.", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Jorge Smith", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "General Manager at Hard Rock Hotel, Pattaya, Thailand, HPL Hotels & Resorts", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jorge-smith-0116017/", "recommendations