ndations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABepTqwBAF2M9v6OdQVt-cbQhxYJnxem0kA", "recommendations/2/context": "Marc worked with María on the same team", "recommendations/2/date": "October 22, 2015", "recommendations/2/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Maria while she was Cruise Manager on the Au Co Cruises, A luxury vessel that she brought at the top.\nMaria was managing the ship at the perfection, building a team spirit and caring her guests on the best way.  \nMaria has a really good eye to details and is very creative, always giving new ideas. Maria highly improved the operations on board. It was a great time to work with Maria as co-workers and also to meet her strong and wonderful personality. I would be very happy to work again with her and strongly recommend her as leader.", "recommendations/2/name": "María Fenollar Gomez", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Business Development Director | Perfumes, Hair & Body Mists & Home Fragrance Manufacturing | From Concept to Market", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maría-fenollar-gomez-04002a98/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABSmJbAB7uZY6FCRAuscywo5JBZxTajjS2Y", "recommendations/3/context": "Marc managed TUAN directly", "recommendations/3/date": "October 15, 2015", "recommendations/3/description": "It was a pleasure to work with Tuan, I saw and participated at his evolution in Bhaya Cruises.\nTuan is a dedicated team member, like accurate work and strong team leader. Evermore Tuan has a great guests caring and is able to front different kinds of situations on board. \nI hope to work again with Tuan as his work is great as his personality. ", "recommendations/3/name": "TUAN NGUYEN VAN", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "General Cruise Manager at Athena Cruise", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tuan-nguyen-van-ab5597102/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABoSKmkB3a1H5VeFutheOmu6rQm3ultvh14", "recommendations/4/context": "Marc reported directly to clement", "recommendations/4/date": "October 15, 2015", "recommendations/4/description": "It was a pleasure to work with Clement in  Bhaya Cruises, we worked very closely for the best improvements of 19 vessels.\nClement was operating on a good ways multi tasks and leading the team with tenacity. Taking decisions and listening/understanding his co-workers.\nI would be happy to be again part of his team in the future.\n", "recommendations/4/name": "clement chin", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Senior Consultant at Asia Sun Relocation", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/clement-chin-9191431a/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPviWUBTMuoG8jFlFes_6sVQsQf8OlCQZA", "recommendations/5/context": "Marc worked with Mikhail but they were at different companies", "recommendations/5/date": "October 13, 2015", "recommendations/5/description": "Mikhail Kostan was employed by our partner TWP co.,ltd Company for a period of six years.\nDuring the time that Mr. Kostan and I worked together, I found him to be very efficient and helpful. I could always count on Mr. Kostan to pitch in where needed, often with very little notice.\nWhile Mr. Kostan was employed by TWP co.,ltd Company, he help us a lot to increase our Russian and CIS market for VIP clients. He know height standards for servicing VIP clients and can provide great service for them.\nMr. Kostan would be a valuable addition to any company he chooses to join, and I have no hesitation in recommending him highly.", "recommendations/5/name": "Mikhail K.", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "AI Business Architect & Innovation Strategist | Turnaround & Growth Strategist | Bridging frontier AI research (LLM efficiency, semantic compression, universal protocols) with proven P&L impact", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mkostan/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAvEg1QBQXpnkKLT0WlPIwLYJ8u8zmQ0LTQ", "recommendations/6/context": "Marc worked with Carlos on the same team", "recommendations/6/date": "September 26, 2015", "recommendations/6/description": "I worked directly with Carlos during our common stay in Bhaya Cruises, on a short time, Carlos could reach a goal on few months that it couldn't be done by others before. He is obstinate to get results on a fast and effective way.\nIt was a pleasure to work with Carlos.", "recommendations/6/name": "Carlos Martin Bregon", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Air Traffic Controller at ENAIRE", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/carlosmartinbregon/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAlB72EBWT957tkoXo-miJavKR6S7JtgqMk", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Alejo worked with Marc on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "June 17, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "It was a totally pleasure to work with Mr. Marc at Bhaya Cruises. During my time working with Marc, he was leading the Quality Control department and I had the opportunity to improved and learned every day many good things from him.\n\nMr. Marc is hard working, dedicated, passionate and extremely professional person at work, who gives 100 % of himself every single day.\n\n I highly recommend Mr. Marc and it will be a totally pleasure to work with him again in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Alejo F. G", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Hospitality Manager and English School Educator", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alejandro-fenollar/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABPOE5MBnzGe4y_s2z8_eFM3hhB2hnyJGv0", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "TUAN worked with Marc on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "October 25, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "that was a great time to work with Marc, beyond a manager he is also my brother, as teacher, he was able to handle any kind of situation was happened on board. myself and friends really hope to work with him a great manager.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "TUAN NGUYEN VAN", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "General Cruise Manager at Athena Cruise", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tuan-nguyen-van-ab5597102/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABoSKmkB3a1H5VeFutheOmu6rQm3ultvh14", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "María was senior to Marc but didn't manage Marc directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "October 23, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "I had the pleasure of working directly with Mr Marc during his time as a Quality Control Manager at Bhaya Cruises.\nMarc is a motivated and responsible person with a high degree of integrity. He had a considerable amount of responsibilities in this role, improving service and maintenance, training managers and staff on board or guest relation and he handled them effortlessly. He takes the initiative to identify problems and devise solutions.\n Marc has the ability to inspire respect and cooperation in teammates, using his strong leadership abilities, logical thinking abilities, and the ability to work well with teams.\nI have enjoyed working with Marc during my 2 years in the company and i would love to have the opportunity to work with him again in the future.\n", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "María Fenollar Gomez", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Business Development Director | Perfumes, Hair & Body Mists & Home Fragrance Manufacturing | From Concept to Market", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maría-fenollar-gomez-04002a98/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABSmJbAB7uZY6FCRAuscywo5JBZxTajjS2Y", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "clement managed Marc directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "October 15, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "It was memorable time working with Marc whilst i was operating Bhaya Cruises -known as the largest cruise fleet in the famous Ha Long Bay. Marc is such a detail QC that made the products in cruising with Bhaya more competitive. We had the best service and Food and Beverage quality too. GCC feed backs with excellence service and lots of happy passengers. you can't wrong with this manager. He shall make it right. recommend him anytime.\n", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "clement chin", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Senior Consultant at Asia Sun Relocation", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/clement-chin-9191431a/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPviWUBTMuoG8jFlFes_6sVQsQf8OlCQZA", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Mikhail worked with Marc but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "October 13, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I am writing this reference letter to recommend Mr. Marc \n\nMr. Marc is a very responsible and dedicated person at work. He can handle multi task at the same time and never lets down our expectation. He is willing to take over new responsibilities at work without hesitation and consistently gives many creative ideas at work. During the time he was working for Phi - Phi The Beach Hotel, our clients was happy and warm welcomed all the time. All gala dinners and special private dinners for our clients was are great. \n\nIt was such a very pleasant and interesting time working with him. I believe he possesses just the skills and qualifications that an exceptional Guest Relation and F&B manager should have as well as of a leader.\n\nI highly recommend Mr. Marc for your company and, without doubt, believe that he will be such a great contribution to yours.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Mikhail K.", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "AI Business Architect & Innovation Strategist | Turnaround & Growth Strategist | Bridging frontier AI research (LLM efficiency, semantic compression, universal protocols) with proven P&L impact", "recommendationsR